; Galaxy
; Four logarithmic spiral arms offset 90 degrees apart,
; each shaded with a different palette color range.
; The spiral equation is: r = t/4, angle = t + offset.

HIDETURTLE
SETPENSIZE 1
SETBACKGROUND "black

TO ARM :offset :cstart
  PENUP
  HOME
  PENDOWN
  FOR [t 1 720] [
    SETPENCOLOR REMAINDER :cstart + :t / 3 256
    SETXY :t / 4 * SIN (:t + :offset)  :t / 4 * COS (:t + :offset)
  ]
  PENUP
END

ARM   0  20
ARM  90 150
ARM 180  90
ARM 270 220
